'''天主教馬德普拉塔教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Maris Platensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de Mar del Plata}}）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教拉普拉塔總教區|拉普拉塔總教區]]。

教區成立於1957年2月11日，<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|date=1957年|volume=49|title=''Quandoquidem adoranda''|page=653|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2049%20%5B1957%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2013-04-09|archive-date=2010-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327070714/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2049%20%5B1957%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>位於[[布宜諾斯艾利斯省|布宜諾斯艾利斯省]]東南部九縣。2004年有教友662,186人（佔轄區總人口80.0%）、五十個堂區、八十七名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|加俾額爾·安多尼·梅斯特雷|Gabriel Antonio Mestre}}<ref name="Vatican20170718">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 18.07.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/07/18/170718a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107034202/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/07/18/170718a.html |archivedate=2019-11-07 |language=en |date=2017-07-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|達里奧·魯本-金塔納|Dario Rubén Quintana}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 05.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/05/191105a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106164523/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/05/191105a.html |archivedate=2019-11-06 |language=en |date=2019-11-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-es|安多尼·馬里諾|Antonio Marino}}<ref name="Vatican20170718" />。

